org.fugerit.java.core.cfg

Interface ConfigurableObject

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    FixedFileFieldValidator, IdGenerator, RequestFilter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractConfigurableObject, AttributeConfig, BasicConfig, CommandConfig, ConnectionFactoryConfig, DataListCatalogConfig, DefaultConfigurableObject, DefaultRequestFilter, FixedFileFieldBasicValidator, FixedFileFieldRegexValidator, Log4JConfig, ModuleConfig, PropertiesConfigurableObject, StatusConfig, VersionConfig, XMLConfigurableObject, XMLSchemaCatalogConfig

    public interface ConfigurableObject

    A class implementing ConfigurableObject interface is an object which could be configured through an XML Document or a Properties object.

    Author:
    Fugerit
